  title={T1 | Environment \& Setup --- Is the System Running?}]
\begin{multicols}{2}
\begin{checklist2}
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] Docker / Kubernetes cluster is running (Online)
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] All pods show status Running (no CrashLoopBackOff)
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] PostgreSQL is accepting connections
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] Neo4j browser opens at localhost:7474 (Online)
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] Redis is responding to PING (Online)
