  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] Kafka brokers are all online (3 of 3) (Online)
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] FastAPI backend returns 200 on /health
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] Node.js orchestration service returns 200 on /api/status
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] React dashboard loads without console errors
  \item React Native app builds without errors
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] SSL/HTTPS is configured on all endpoints
  \item[\textcolor{checkgreen}{\ding{51}}] Environment variables are loaded (no missing keys)
